        "rich_text_fcU3Qe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why the Left Hand?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Why the Left Hand?</h3><p>The left hand became widely accepted because it symbolizes love, commitment, and emotional connection. Today, it remains the most common choice for women who follow which hand to wear engagement ring customs.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_6zLWHM": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Which Finger to Wear the Engagement Ring On?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Which Finger to Wear the Engagement Ring On?</h2>",
            "custom_id": "which",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_W7BQmF": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Which_Finger_to_Wear_the_Engagement_Ring_On.jpg",
            "text": "<h3>The Ring Finger and Its Significance</h3><p>The fourth finger of the left hand is known globally as the engagement ring finger. Most couples choose this finger because it represents loyalty, affection, and a promise of marriage.</p><p>If you're currently selecting your ring, you can explore modern styles designed for elegance and comfort through collections like Lucira Jewelry’s<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-ring\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">engagement ring</span></a> selection.</p><h3>Is It Acceptable to Wear It on Another Finger?</h3><p>Absolutely. Cultural customs, lifestyle, and comfort all influence where to wear engagement ring pieces. Some women prefer a different finger due to work requirements, hand dominance, or personal expression.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "column",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "0-306ct-half-eternity-pave-diamond-band",
