        "rich_text_xii4nX": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Modern Variations: Choosing What Works for You",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Modern Variations: Choosing What Works for You</h2><h3>Couples Choosing Matching Styles</h3><p>A modern trend is choosing matching or coordinated<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/couple-rings\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">couple rings</span></a> as a symbol of unity and partnership.</p><h3>Rings for Every Identity</h3><p>Today, designs for an<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/mens-engagement-rings\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">engagement ring for men</span></a> are equally sophisticated and meaningful, reflecting evolving traditions.<br/> Women also enjoy a wide variety of elegant options—explore curated selections of<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings-for-women\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">engagement ring for women</span></a> to find the perfect match for your style.</p>",
            "custom_id": "modern",
