          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Choosing_the_Right_Engagement_Ring_for_Your_Hand.jpg",
            "text": "<h3>Hand Shape and Ring Style</h3><p>Different finger lengths and hand shapes pair better with certain designs. For example:</p><ul><li>Slim fingers often pair beautifully with solitaires.<br/><br/></li><li>Wide fingers may suit halo or multi-stone designs.<br/><br/></li><li>Petite hands benefit from refined, delicate settings.<br/><br/></li></ul><h3>Comfort and Everyday Wear</h3><p>Since an engagement ring is worn daily, choosing a setting that fits comfortably is essential. Consider metal durability, prong style, and gemstone height.</p>",
